position = Vector2(336, 46)
text = ["I see that you've found your way in here.", "But, if you have come to rescue me, I'm afraid that you are far too late.", "Just look at me... I'm nothing but a pile of bones now...", "Waiting to wither away. Just like everyone else here.", "But... Enough about my meaningless self.", "What's left of my vision tells me that you're not looking too good yourself.", "And if you've come all this way, you must be looking for something...", "Something old... Something used...", "...", "Hmm...", "Well, let's just say that your time is almost up.", "You better hurry."]
